  "prompt": "Which are the best ad agencies in Barcelona?",
  "response": "Barcelona is home to several top-tier advertising agencies known for their creativity, innovation, and impactful campaigns. Some of the best ad agencies in Barcelona include:\n\n1. **FCB Global** - Known for its strategic approach and creativity, FCB Global has a strong presence in Barcelona with a focus on impactful and innovative advertising.\n\n2. **SCPF** - An internationally acclaimed agency, SCPF is recognized for its creative excellence and ability to craft compelling stories that resonate with audiences.\n\n3. **McCann Barcelona** - Part of the global McCann network, this agency is renowned for its strategic insights and exceptional creativity in advertising.\n\n4. **Proximity Barcelona** - Specializing in data-driven marketing and personalized campaigns, Proximity Barcelona is a leader in creating highly effective and targeted advertising.\n\n5. **David The Agency** - Known for its bold and cutting-edge campaigns, David The Agency has made a significant mark in the advertising world with offices in Barcelona.\n\n6. **La Despensa Ingredientes Creativos** - This agency prides itself on creative innovation and has a reputation for developing unique and memorable campaigns.\n\n7. **RK People** - A full-service advertising agency in Barcelona, RK People combines creativity with strategic thinking to deliver impactful campaigns.\n\n8. **VIVID Brand Content** - Specializing in content creation and brand storytelling, VIVID Brand Content is known for its ability to connect brands with their audiences in meaningful ways.\n\nRemember that the best agency for a specific project might vary based on the type of campaign, industry, and specific needs. It is often a good idea to look at recent work, client testimonials, and industry awards to get a sense of an agency's strengths and suitability for your project.",
